subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
It's me Russell Robinson, i write to bring good news to you that UBS Swiss has
initiated your fund USD$45 Million approval transfer and attached is
the electronic
fund approval transfer programmed system report.
Get back to me as quickly as possible for further directives.
Best regards
Russell Robinson

subject: Re: Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Russell Robinson,

Thank you for your message. It's quite exciting to hear about this fund approval transfer. Could you please provide more details about it? How did this come about and what does it entail?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Walter

subject: Re: Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Mr Walter,

In response to your mail, kindly note that the only way for you to receive
the fund without any stop order from any money monitoring agency is for me
to use my organisation to represent you as our beneficiary as i have
already did in my request and has been approved by the UBS Swiss .

below is my web page  again ;

https://www.americanprogress.org/people/robinson-russell/

With this arrangement, you will receive the fund via   tbank withdrawal
instrument  ATM card and also  will  be process and send to your nominated
address in your country through express delivery service by their
accredited courier firm.

Further note note ATM card  bank withdrawal instrument will arrive before
the 5 days  and this will enable you start making withdrawal of cash from
any ATM machine around you and this will be based on the daily withdrawal
limit which is $15,000.00 dollar's which comes in three different
transaction of $5,000.00 dollars each.

But bear in mind that the UBS Swiss bank require  that we pay the
processing of the fund release upfront charges which $18,090.00 dollars and
this  will be taken care by me through my organisation accredited fiduciary
agent while you  will have to take care of the  outstanding balance is
$4,975.00 dollars only.

On this noted, I will use my organisation accredited fiduciary agent   to
pay part upfront payment for them to start up the process and completed,
and all legal documents issues ,I will send it to you for your preview and
record too and  you will then take care of the outstanding balance
$4,975.00 dollars  so that they can immediately effects the  sending of
the  ATM card  bank withdrawal instrument to you at once for your immediate
use for cash withdrawal

I attached here my I'd card for your preview and record too.

In this regards, I urge you to get back to me now and let me know if I
should proceed with this arrangement.
Best regards
Russell *Robinson**W**a*

subject: Re: Fwd: Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Mr. Robinson,

Thank you for your detailed response. I appreciate the time and effort you've put into explaining this process to me. 

I'm intrigued by the ATM card bank withdrawal instrument you mentioned. Could you please elaborate more on how it works? Also, I'm curious about the daily withdrawal limit of dollars, is there a reason why it's set at that specific amount?

Regarding the processing fee, could you provide more information on what exactly this fee covers? And why is there a need for me to cover part of it?

I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Walter

subject: Re: Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Walter,

In response to your email, I am surprised that you don't know about bank
withdrawal instrument  ATM card, anyway bank ATM card works as simple as
once you receive it , take to any ATM machine around you and slort it into
the machine and press the amount you want to withdraw and then press your
secret pin code four digits number and wait for a few minutes and then
amount will be despence out for your cash collection.

Further more, the withdrawal limit is programmed in such a way that you
don't pay high taxation withdrawal charges when ever you perform a
withdrawal transaction.
.
On the issue of the processing fee, note that this fee covers all legal
clearance documents as required by the government monentay authorities in
order to avoid any government agency to put a stop order on the fund
release to you..

Also, on the issue of you  covering the outstanding balance is because i
could not get the total amount required through my organisation agent who
will be paying for the upfront payment fee as I stated iny previous email.

I hope the above details explanation and information have given a direct
and clear answer to your questions while I wait for your immediate response
with your required informatios and confirm your readiness for us to move
forward .

Yours sincerely brother
Mr Russell Robinson
